### FAKKE NEWS API Tests
### Base URL: https://localhost:7000 (ajustar según tu puerto)

### ============================================
### CATEGORIES TESTS
### ============================================

### GET All Categories
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Categories
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Category by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Categories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### POST Create New Category
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deportes"
}

###

### PUT Update Category
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/Categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Política Actualizada"
}

###

### DELETE Category
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/Categories/999
Accept: application/json

